<br>
I did, and I offered to pay a lot for spells. <br>
<br>
/auction Paying 15,000 plat for Mask of the Hunter<br>
<br>
Within 10 seconds I got a /tell from the spell master of a guild who sold me his guilds copy, at the expense of his guild druids. His feeling was that the cash was more important to the guild then one of their druid's with that spell.<br>
<br>
True story. Told a couple friends in the same boat- they did the same thing, and also had rapid successs.<br>
<br>
The spells are out there- you just need to get a person's attention.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urheawindsong.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhea Windsong</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/12/01 8:01:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2480.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to get rare spells</span><hr size=1> thats terrible that he would sell them over giving it to a guild druid who could use. I would /guildremove from a guild like that. <p><img src=http://members.theglobe.com/Rhea69/RHEATAG2.JPG></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urhesolooshun.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhes Olooshun</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/12/01 8:01:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2480.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to get rare spells</span><hr size=1> Only problem with that is, not everyone has money.  Personally, I have found that trading spells for spells works quite well.  I recently traded a second copy of Fist of Karana for Protection of the Glades.  I also was able to get Succor from a kind cleric for a copy of Mark of Karn.  It just goes to show that money isn't necessarily everything. <p><a href="http://worldzone.net/"target="web"><img src="http://worldzone.net/themes/azyn//sig2.GIF"border="0"</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udreth1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dreth1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/12/01 8:08:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2480.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to get rare spells</span><hr size=1> Oh, I agree about trading rare spells for rare spells. But you gotta HAVE those rare spells first, and then find someone who wants it who has access to what you need. Everyone needs $$$.<br>
<br>
The money thing is a last resort. But, if you've been raiding/looking for months...remember there are a lot of druids to compete with out there.<br>
<br>
The guy in question is a good guy, in response to #2. He is on eof the guild leaders, and put the needs of the guild first- they needed $$$, not spells that didn't benefit the guild as a whole. I'm sure it wouldn't have worked with a spell like Mark of Karn, Naltron's Mark, whatever. But let's not fool ourselves into thinking a spell like Mask of the Hunter helps the guild as a whole :)<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uphreaky.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Phreaky</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/12/01 12:02:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2480.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.dunko.net/greg/misc/fat.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to get rare spells</span><hr size=1> lol.  It would take you like an hour tops to form up a group or two to kill AW and GW in skyfire to get these spells.  Why spend 15K?   Heck, you'll get EXTRA lvl 59-60 spells to give to guildmates or sell off for money in your guild.<br>
<br>
I don't blame that guildleader one bit.  These spells are easy to get (easier than 55-58 imo).  It could easily be replaced before guild druids need it and the guild just made a sizeable chunk of change. <p><img src=http://people.ne.mediaone.net/dunko/eqimages/phreaky.gif ALIGN=LEFT>
